{"tid":761954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貿易戰有解？美國將立即與歐盟展開新的貿易談判","createTime":"2018-07-31T00:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T10:50:43.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8a7a7de2554c1732e7124e53952448a2ab5ec59d","tid":761954,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:06:09.000Z","msg":"貿易戰有解？美國將立即與歐盟展開新的貿易談判<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4175399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4175399&d=M%2Byt0bQfKqdzmRiA4u4ggf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=bb2310e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4175399</a><br />\n<br />\n根據 MarketWatch 分析報導，一名川普政府高官週日說，美國將立即與歐盟展開協商，期望能就農產品與能源產品，達成貿易協定，立刻進行實際銷售，以賣出更多黃豆，牛肉與液化天然氣至歐洲國家。<br />\n<br />\n川普總統的首席經濟顧問庫卓 (Larry Kudlow) 說，他將會參與這項由美國貿易代表 Robert Lighthizer 所領導的協商。<br />\n<br />\n「我們將立即展開協商，」庫卓在接受 CBS 電視台訪問時說。「我們將分門別類，檢視所有不同領域。」<br />\n<br />\n庫卓強調，在農產品方面的廣泛討論，是這項雙邊談判的一部份。這突顯了與布魯塞爾方面的歧見，歐盟曾誓言不談農產品。"},{"pid":"43c13c7d69a89558fc1e2dce89e54ae17ff9d0b3","tid":761954,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efccf8871540f8921161c85b1055e324a06e30f3","tid":761954,"uid":55257,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:07:43.000Z","msg":"分析指，中国或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"d863920628ddc53276663a3965cc525eac00f877","tid":761954,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:24:53.000Z","msg":"美墨NAFTA協商 力促8月完成重大議題修訂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2503418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2503418&d=M%2Byt0bQfKqdzmRiA4u4ggf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=441df0fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2503418&h=7239162e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2503418</a><br />\n<br />\n〔編譯胡志愷／綜合報導〕北美自由貿易協定（NAFTA）協商有望重啟，美國、墨西哥於上週末再度會談，兩國力促加速NAFTA修訂進度，希望在8月底前可以完成重要議題協議，預計協商團隊可以在近期展開正式協商。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">墨西哥經濟部長瓜賈度（Ildefonso Guajardo）上週末和美國貿易代表萊席爾（Robert Lighthizer）以及總統川普女婿庫什納（Jared Kushner）會面，會議結束後瓜賈度表示他們進行了一場「有建設性」、「非常正向」的會談，同時也向記者透露，他和萊席爾達成了8月份完成重要議題協商的共識，力促NAFTA加速修訂。<br />\n<br />\n對此美國貿易代表也表示，他們希望可以在8月份時和墨西哥達成修訂共識，而這個共識同時也是加拿大可以接受的。</span><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥新統總羅培茲（Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador）和川普的信件於上星期公開，而川普也回信墨國，表示如果NAFTA快速完成協商，可以提升兩國邊境的工作機會、提升薪資水平。<br />\n<br />\nNAFTA參與國共有美國、墨西哥、加拿大3國，儘管美國傾向分別和加墨雙邊會談，而目前又以美墨兩方積極的接觸，不過墨西哥和加拿大稍早也曾發聲明指出，NAFTA協商必須是3方會談，不會接受雙邊會談的形式。<br />\n<br />\nNAFTA協商因美國取消鋼鋁稅豁免而擱置，日前協商主要卡在汽車議題，以及美國堅持加入「日落條款」（Sunset clause）兩大問題上。"},{"pid":"566901430794cb68d7a61b4ef8a5a1d4c287f92a","tid":761954,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:45:33.000Z","msg":"侵帝好撚勁  由頭帶到尾"},{"pid":"a5426766d071f9ccb759fd6711469c759438993e","tid":761954,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:46:44.000Z","msg":"Marco Rubio<br />\n@marcorubio<br />\n&middot;<br />\n26 Jul<br />\nHopeful that the trade truce between the U.S. &amp; EU will be followed by a deal on NAFTA &amp; with Japan, so we can unite with them to confront the real threat, #China&rsquo;s unfair,deceptive &amp; illegal trade practices."},{"pid":"70ea2e5196271fb9dbd1fb79709b9b5b137f175c","tid":761954,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"566901430794cb68d7a61b4ef8a5a1d4c287f92a","tid":761954,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:45:33.000Z","msg":"侵帝好撚勁  由頭帶到尾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:49:06.000Z","msg":"我地唔可以咁輕敵，我地要用「中或贏」角度去睇件事，侵侵俾習帝迫到周圍同人妥協。"},{"pid":"69db7ad20dc957dc5f04a7d18f775e127f3cd9d5","tid":761954,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5426766d071f9ccb759fd6711469c759438993e","tid":761954,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:46:44.000Z","msg":"Marco Rubio<br />\n@marcorubio<br />\n&middot;<br />\n26 Jul<br />\nHopeful that the trade truce between the U.S. &amp; EU will be followed by a deal on NAFTA &amp; with Japan, so we can unite with them to confront the real threat, #China&rsquo;s unfair,deceptive &amp; illegal trade practices."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:49:09.000Z","msg":"講到明集火力屌中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60964836679740b9f81be4ed61e83e1b9afffb04","tid":761954,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:51:50.000Z","msg":"土木巴真係勤力<br />\n日日都有得睇好消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3649848a18a6a7cfcaf7897cd41023560d1a39c5","tid":761954,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:53:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c991344e9f38dd1099971b3a484623b2be485060","tid":761954,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"60964836679740b9f81be4ed61e83e1b9afffb04","tid":761954,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:51:50.000Z","msg":"土木巴真係勤力<br />\n日日都有得睇好消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T01:03:37.000Z","msg":"朝早返工坐車就係google美國中國，睇下有咩好消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb28666fb2059dd8ca3a40c525b45cc30beb8374","tid":761954,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T01:06:10.000Z","msg":"等睇加拿大條左膠總統跪低  之前唔係好臭串？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b